01:16:39,804 --> 01:16:42,514
listened to "Asleep," wrote a poem—

1301
01:16:42,598 --> 01:16:44,641
Fine. Okay. Your turn.

1302
01:16:46,936 --> 01:16:48,436
Hmm.

1303
01:16:50,356 --> 01:16:51,564
Yeah. I've got one.

1304
01:16:53,859 --> 01:16:55,318
Well...

1305
01:16:55,403 --> 01:16:57,237
there's this one guy.

1306
01:16:57,321 --> 01:17:00,073
Queer as a 3-dollar bill.

1307
01:17:00,157 --> 01:17:04,035
The guy's father doesn't know about his son.

1308
01:17:04,120 --> 01:17:09,374
So he comes into the basement
one night when he's supposed to be out oftown.

1309
01:17:09,458 --> 01:17:11,584
Catches his son with another boy.

1310
01:17:13,087 --> 01:17:14,796
So he starts beating him.

1311
01:17:14,880 --> 01:17:18,883
But not like the slap kind. Like, the real kind.

1312
01:17:22,054 --> 01:17:26,725
And the boyfriend says,
"Stop. You're killing him."

1313
01:17:28,019 --> 01:17:30,603
But the son just yells, "Get out."

1314
01:17:31,981 --> 01:17:35,108
And eventually...

1315
01:17:36,527 --> 01:17:39,571
the boyfriend just did.

1316
01:17:46,245 --> 01:17:48,371
Why can't you save anybody?

1317
01:17:50,666 --> 01:17:52,125
I don't know.

1318
01:17:54,462 --> 01:17:55,754
Forget it.

1319
01:17:56,797 --> 01:17:58,840
I'm free now, right?

1320
01:17:58,924 --> 01:18:02,927
I could meet
the love of my life any second.

1321
01:18:03,012 --> 01:18:06,556
Things will be different now and that's good.

1322
01:18:06,640 --> 01:18:08,933
I just need to meet a good guy.

1323
01:18:09,852 --> 01:18:10,977
Yeah.

1324
01:18:24,533 --> 01:18:26,034
[ Patrick ]
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

1325
01:18:27,953 --> 01:18:29,162
It's all right.

1326
01:18:33,876 --> 01:18:37,295
[ Charlie ]
I've been spending a lot oftime with Patrick.

1327
01:18:37,380 --> 01:18:40,673
He begins every night really excited.

1328
01:18:40,758 --> 01:18:44,761
He always says he feels free
and tonight is his destiny.

1329
01:18:44,845 --> 01:18:48,515
But after a while he runs out ofthings
to keep himself numb.

1330
01:18:50,935 --> 01:18:53,812
And Sam got her letter from Penn State.

1331
01:19:00,194 --> 01:19:02,445
"We will require you to take
our summer session...

1332
01:19:02,530 --> 01:19:06,199
at the main campus immediately following
your high school graduation."

1333
01:19:09,412 --> 01:19:10,662
She got in, Charlie.

1334
01:19:16,669 --> 01:19:17,669
