1344
01:19:54,999 --> 01:19:59,127
Especially because,
ever since I blacked out in the cafeteria...

1345
01:19:59,211 --> 01:20:00,795
it's been getting worse.

1346
01:20:00,880 --> 01:20:03,965
And I can't turn it offthis time.

1347
01:20:04,049 --> 01:20:08,094
All right, guys, you wanna pass
your copies of Gatsby up to the front, please.

1348
01:20:08,179 --> 01:20:10,096
And I know it's the last day...

1349
01:20:10,181 --> 01:20:13,933
but ifwe could keep it to a dull roar,
I'd appreciate it.

1350
01:20:14,018 --> 01:20:15,018
