1351
01:20:15,102 --> 01:20:18,605
Guy. Guys. Thankyou for such a great year.

1352
01:20:18,689 --> 01:20:20,565
I had a blast. I hope you did, too.

1353
01:20:20,649 --> 01:20:23,526
And I hope you have
a great time this summer on your vacations.

1354
01:20:23,611 --> 01:20:25,904
Now who here is gonna read
for pleasure this summer?

1355
01:20:31,452 --> 01:20:32,702
