- [ All Cheering ]

1378
01:21:50,990 --> 01:21:52,532
[ Charlie ]
Dear friend...

1379
01:21:52,616 --> 01:21:55,159
I wanted to tell you about us running.

1380
01:21:55,244 --> 01:21:57,036
There was this beautiful sunset.

1381
01:21:57,121 --> 01:21:59,455
And just a few hours before, everyone I love...

1382
01:21:59,540 --> 01:22:02,166
had their last day of high school ever.

1383
01:22:02,251 --> 01:22:04,210
I was happy because they were happy...

1384
01:22:04,295 --> 01:22:06,629
even though I counted and I have...

1385
01:22:06,714 --> 01:22:10,925
1 ,095 days to go.

1386
01:22:11,010 --> 01:22:13,428
I kept imagining
what school would be like without them...

1387
01:22:13,512 --> 01:22:16,180
as they were all getting ready
for their prom.

1388
01:22:16,265 --> 01:22:19,642
My sister finally decided
to break up with Derek...

1389
01:22:19,727 --> 01:22:22,145
and go stag with her girlfriends instead.

1390
01:22:24,398 --> 01:22:26,649
And then there was Sam.

1391
01:22:26,734 --> 01:22:30,069
I've looked at her picture since that night.

1392
01:22:30,154 --> 01:22:33,489
I like to see how happy she was
before she knew.

1393
01:22:33,574 --> 01:22:37,452
They were in a hotel suite after prom
and the truth came out.

1394
01:22:37,536 --> 01:22:41,456
Basically Craig
has been cheating on Sam the whole time.

1395
01:22:41,540 --> 01:22:43,291
When I heard that...

1396
01:22:43,375 --> 01:22:45,960
I kept thinking about the happy girl
in these pictures.

1397
01:22:46,045 --> 01:22:49,839
'Cause she doesn't have 1 ,095 days to go.

1398
01:22:49,923 --> 01:22:51,841
She made it.

1399
01:22:51,925 --> 01:22:54,135
This is her time.

1400
