1404
01:23:04,396 --> 01:23:06,397
Ooh! Get against the railing
and try to look suave.

1405
01:23:06,482 --> 01:23:08,941
Yep, this is the one.
That's gonna be a great angle.

1406
01:23:12,196 --> 01:23:13,780
[ Ticking ]

